{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-post-js","path":"/antibiotiklar/","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"Koronavirus ilmiy tadqiqotlari o'zbek tilida"}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"02865952-b427-5314-a676-1513c0e636b8","excerpt":"Yo’q. Antibiotiklar viruslarga qarshi foyda bermaydi. Ular faqatgina bakterial infektsiyalar uchun ishlatiladi. COVID-19 virusdan kelib chiqadi, shuning uchun…","html":"<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 590px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/bloglar/static/27e20e06cded4baf733b4e22590ca9c5/f058b/antibiotic.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 60.13513513513513%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"Chinese Salty Egg\"\n        title=\"Chinese Salty Egg\"\n        src=\"/bloglar/static/27e20e06cded4baf733b4e22590ca9c5/fcda8/antibiotic.png\"\n        srcset=\"/bloglar/static/27e20e06cded4baf733b4e22590ca9c5/12f09/antibiotic.png 148w,\n/bloglar/static/27e20e06cded4baf733b4e22590ca9c5/e4a3f/antibiotic.png 295w,\n/bloglar/static/27e20e06cded4baf733b4e22590ca9c5/fcda8/antibiotic.png 590w,\n/bloglar/static/27e20e06cded4baf733b4e22590ca9c5/f058b/antibiotic.png 630w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>Yo’q. Antibiotiklar viruslarga qarshi foyda bermaydi. Ular faqatgina bakterial infektsiyalar uchun ishlatiladi. COVID-19 virusdan kelib chiqadi, shuning uchun antibiotiklar xech qanday davoga ega emas. Antibiotiklar COVID-19 ning oldini olish yoki davolash vositasi sifatida ishlatilmasligi kerak. Kasalxonalarda shifokorlar ba’zida og’ir kasal bemorlarga COVID-19 asoratlariga olib keladigan ikkilamchi bakterial infektsiyalarni oldini olish yoki davolash uchun antibiotiklardan foydalanishadi. Ular <strong>faqat bakterial infektsiyani</strong> davolash uchun <strong>shifokor ko’rsatmasi</strong> bo’yicha <strong>qo’llanilishi kerak</strong>.</p>\n<h6>Muallifdan:</h6>\n<p>Ushbu maqola JSST tashkilotining <a href=\"https://www.who.int/emergencies/diseases/novel-coronavirus-2019/question-and-answers-hub/q-a-detail/q-a-coronaviruses\">ushbu saxifasi</a> tarjimasi bo’lib, davolanishdan avval albatta shifokor bilan maslaxatlashishingizni so’raymiz. Xatolar va kamchiliklarini ushbu pochtaga yuborishingiz mumkin <strong>muslimchik.inha@gmail.com</strong></p>","frontmatter":{"title":"Antibiotiklar foydalimi?","date":"July 20, 2020","description":""}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/antibiotiklar/","previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/deksametazon/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Buyuk Britaniya olimlarining deksametazon ustida olib borgan ilmiy ishlari natijalari"}},"next":{"fields":{"slug":"/avigan/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Yaponiyaning 'Avigan' deb nomlanuvchi antibiotiki qanchalik foydali?"}}}}}